      "descriptionJa": "グラフ探索、最短路アルゴリズム、全域木アルゴリズム、トポロジカルソート、グラフ構造判定。",
      "descriptionEn": "Graph search, shortest-path algorithms, spanning-tree algorithms, topological sorting, and graph-structure tests."
    },
    "Discrete-Mathematics.Set-Theory": {
